@node "Purpose" "What to do with it"

@{b}Purpose@{ub}
~~~~~~~
  SGrab is a utility which allows you to save screens or windows as
  ILBM or JPEG files.
  SGrab supports all display-modes provided by p96/cgfx or by the native
  chipsets.

  This program is based on Stefan Proels' great CyberGrab. I decided to
  write a new grabber, because Stefan lost the source code of CyberGrab
  so that he isn't able to make changes to it :(

@endnode


